# The real printer config carries the Bambu serial + LAN access code. It is
# git-ignored and must not be baked into an image layer either — compose mounts
# it as a read-only volume at runtime (PRINTERS_CONFIG_PATH=/app/config/printers.json).
# The committed printers.example.json is still copied so the image is self-describing.
config/printers.json
